# SQL → Prisma Converter: Project Overview

This repository implements a real‑time PostgreSQL SQL → Prisma schema converter.

- Main page: [src/pages/converter.tsx](mdc:src/pages/converter.tsx)
- Core services: [src/services/sql-parser.ts](mdc:src/services/sql-parser.ts), [src/services/prisma-generator.ts](mdc:src/services/prisma-generator.ts)
- Types: [src/types/index.ts](mdc:src/types/index.ts)
- Docs: [README.md](mdc:README.md), [CLAUDE.md](mdc:CLAUDE.md)

## Quick start

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

Open `http://localhost:5173`.

## Tech stack

- React 18 + TypeScript + Vite
- UI: shadcn/ui + Radix UI + Tailwind CSS
- Editor: Monaco Editor (custom Prisma language + `prisma-theme`)
- Path alias: `@` → `./src`

## Project structure

```
src/
├─ components/ui/      # shadcn/ui components
├─ hooks/              # custom hooks
├─ lib/                # utilities
├─ pages/              # routes (converter UI)
├─ services/           # SQL parsing + Prisma generation
├─ types/              # shared TypeScript types
└─ App.tsx             # application shell
```
